<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 12:24:09 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>猪肉出口竞争对手可能受益于中欧贸易紧张局势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/rival-pork-exporters-could-benefit-china-eu-trade-tensions-2024-06-17/</link><description>贸易商和分析师表示，如果北京因贸易紧张局势升级而限制从欧盟的进口，来自南美和美国的猪肉供应商可能会在中国获得市场份额。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 12:16:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/rival-pork-exporters-could-benefit-china-eu-trade-tensions-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称抵制中国在南海的“鲁莽行为”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-resist-chinas-reckless-behaviour-south-china-sea-2024-06-17/</link><description>菲律宾国防部长周一表示，该国武装部队将抵制中国在马尼拉声称拥有主权的南海领土上的“危险和鲁莽行为”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 12:07:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-resist-chinas-reckless-behaviour-south-china-sea-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>阿迪达斯股价因中国腐败指控调查而下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/adidas-shares-fall-investigation-into-china-corruption-allegation-2024-06-17/</link><description>德国运动服装品牌阿迪达斯在收到匿名信后表示正在调查中国的腐败指控，周一该公司股价下跌 4%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 11:40:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/adidas-shares-fall-investigation-into-china-corruption-allegation-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>普京将于6月18日至19日访问朝鲜金正恩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russias-putin-visit-north-korea-june-18-19-2024-06-17/</link><description>克里姆林宫表示，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京将于周二和周三访问朝鲜，这是一次罕见的访问，突显了莫斯科与这个隐居的核武器国家迅速发展的伙伴关系。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 11:14:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russias-putin-visit-north-korea-june-18-19-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>美国、加拿大、日本和菲律宾在南海举行演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-canada-japan-philippines-conduct-exercises-south-china-sea-2024-06-17/</link><description>美国太平洋舰队周一在其网站上表示，美国、加拿大、日本和菲律宾在马尼拉南海专属经济区进行了为期两天的联合海上演习。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 10:43:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-canada-japan-philippines-conduct-exercises-south-china-sea-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国宣布猪肉反倾销调查后西班牙寻求避免贸易战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/spain-calls-negotiations-after-china-announces-eu-pork-anti-dumping-probe-2024-06-17/</link><description>欧盟主要猪肉出口国西班牙周一表示，在北京表示将启动反倾销调查后，该国正在与欧盟官员合作，以避免破坏性关税。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 10:21:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/spain-calls-negotiations-after-china-announces-eu-pork-anti-dumping-probe-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美国的乐观情绪关注法国的焦虑，中国的国内困境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-graphics-2024-06-17/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 10:09:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-graphics-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>伯克希尔哈撒韦公司出售价值3980万美元的中国比亚迪股份</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/berkshire-hathaway-sells-398-mln-shares-chinas-byd-2024-06-17/</link><description>周一向证券交易所提交的文件显示，沃伦·巴菲特旗下的伯克希尔·哈撒韦公司已出售 130 万股电动汽车制造商比亚迪在香港上市的股票，售价为 3.105 亿港元（合 3,980 万美元）。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 09:43:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/berkshire-hathaway-sells-398-mln-shares-chinas-byd-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>巴西加入竞争以放松中国对稀土行业的控制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/brazil-joins-race-loosen-chinas-grip-rare-earths-industry-2024-06-17/</link><description>随着西方经济体努力获取用于绿色能源和国防的磁铁所需的金属，并打破中国在供应链中的主导地位，矿业巨头巴西雄心勃勃地建立稀土行业。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 08:57:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/brazil-joins-race-loosen-chinas-grip-rare-earths-industry-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国对欧洲猪肉展开针锋相对的反倾销立案调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-opens-anti-dumping-probe-into-imported-pork-by-products-eu-2024-06-17/</link><description>中国已对来自欧盟的进口猪肉及其副产品启动反倾销调查，此举似乎主要针对西班牙、荷兰和丹麦，以回应其电动汽车出口的限制。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 07:54:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-opens-anti-dumping-probe-into-imported-pork-by-products-eu-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>韩国将于周二与中国举行首轮会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/south-korea-hold-first-round-talks-with-china-tues-2024-06-17/</link><description>首尔外交部周一表示，根据两国上个月达成的协议，韩国和中国将于周二举行第一轮外交和安全对话。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 07:41:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/south-korea-hold-first-round-talks-with-china-tues-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>瑞典 Essity 上调维达出售后利润率目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/swedens-essity-raises-margin-target-after-vinda-sale-2024-06-17/</link><description>瑞典卫生用品制造商Essity周一上调了核心利润率目标，并重申了撤资香港上市子公司维达（3331.HK）后的核心销售目标。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 06:22:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/swedens-essity-raises-margin-target-after-vinda-sale-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>杰富瑞表示，中国零跑汽车开始在 Stellantis 波兰工厂生产电动汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-leapmotor-started-ev-production-stellantis-polish-plant-jefferies-says-2024-06-17/</link><description>杰富瑞分析师援引零跑汽车管理层的话说，由Stellantis牵头的合资企业已开始在Stellantis位于波兰蒂黑的工厂生产中国零跑汽车的电动汽车。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 05:54:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-leapmotor-started-ev-production-stellantis-polish-plant-jefferies-says-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>VDMA称德国机器人行业面临来自中国的激烈竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/german-robotics-industry-faces-stiff-competition-china-vdma-says-2024-06-17/</link><description>VDMA工程协会的一位代表告诉路透社，来自中国日益激烈的竞争正在给德国机器人行业的前景带来压力，德国机器人行业已经在国内经济疲软的情况下陷入订单下降的困境。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 05:36:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/german-robotics-industry-faces-stiff-competition-china-vdma-says-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>早申：法国队自摆乌龙，中国队未能欢呼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-06-17/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 04:33:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-06-17/</guid></item></channel></rss>